 Test_GETVideos_Pagination‚Üź{
‚ćĚ Test boundary invariants of /videos?per_page=N&page=M pagination metadata
     H‚Üź##.##.##.HttpCommand
     Assert‚Üź##.Assert

     ‚ćĚ Page 1 with a small per_page
     pp‚Üź5
     res‚ÜźH.GetJSON'GET'(‚ćĶ,'/videos?per_page=',‚ćēpp)
     200‚Č†res.HttpStatus:0
     0‚ąä‚ćīres.Data:0
     d‚Üźres.Data

     Assert d.per_page‚Č§pp:                 ‚ćĚ per_page never exceeds requested
     Assert d.first_page=1:                ‚ćĚ first page is always 1
     Assert d.current_page‚Č•d.first_page:   ‚ćĚ current page ‚Č• first page
     Assert d.current_page‚Č§d.last_page:    ‚ćĚ current page ‚Č§ last page
     Assert d.from‚Č•1:                      ‚ćĚ from index ‚Č• 1
     Assert d.to‚Č§d.total:                  ‚ćĚ to index ‚Č§ total
     Assert d.from‚Č§d.to:                   ‚ćĚ from ‚Č§ to
     Assert(‚ČĘd.data)‚Č§d.per_page:           ‚ćĚ data length ‚Č§ per_page
     Assert(‚ČĘd.data)=d.to-d.from-1:        ‚ćĚ data length matches from..to range

     ‚ćĚ Last page: request beyond total to hit the cap
     lp‚Üźd.last_page
     res‚ÜźH.GetJSON'GET'(‚ćĶ,'/videos?per_page=',(‚ćēpp),'&page=',‚ćēlp)
     200‚Č†res.HttpStatus:0
     d‚Üźres.Data

     Assert d.current_page=lp:        ‚ćĚ landed on last page
     Assert d.to=d.total:             ‚ćĚ last page ends at total
     Assert(‚ČĘd.data)‚Č§d.per_page:      ‚ćĚ last page data ‚Č§ per_page
     Assert(‚ČĘd.data)=d.to-d.from-1:   ‚ćĚ data length matches range

     ‚ćĚ Page beyond last should clamp to last page
     res‚ÜźH.GetJSON'GET'(‚ćĶ,'/videos?per_page=',(‚ćēpp),'&page=',‚ćēlp+1)
     200‚Č†res.HttpStatus:0
     Assert res.Data.current_page=lp:   ‚ćĚ clamped to last page

     1
